headline: MAA Announces Taxable Composition of 2025 Distributions
summary: Mid-America Apartment Communities, Inc. or MAA (NYSE: MAA) today announced the taxable composition of the 2025 distributions paid to shareholders. The company does not expect any portion of the 2025 distributions paid to shareholders to represent a return of capital. The company did not incur any foreign taxes.
